WEBVTT

00:03.006 --> 00:06.675
Okay. Our special holiday family and
friends night is coming up Christmas Eve,

00:06.677 --> 00:10.779
and we think it would be really fun to
perform a song we all write together.

00:10.781 --> 00:13.215
So let's throw out words that
make us think of Christmas.

00:13.217 --> 00:14.282
Anybody?

00:15.485 --> 00:17.219
Christmas!

00:18.822 --> 00:22.724
Okay, Herman, the word Christmas
does make me think of Christmas.

00:22.726 --> 00:24.626
Uh, anybody else?

00:26.629 --> 00:27.863
Christmas.

00:29.332 --> 00:30.966
Yeah, Dez, that's
already on the list.

00:30.968 --> 00:32.000
Aw.

00:32.002 --> 00:33.301
What about something
like mistletoe?

00:33.303 --> 00:34.469
Or sleigh bells.

00:34.471 --> 00:36.338
Or presents.

00:36.340 --> 00:39.941
More specifically, the cheetah print
handbag I emailed you all about.

00:40.910 --> 00:42.511
Several times.

00:42.513 --> 00:43.879
Anybody else?

00:45.381 --> 00:48.083
Lily, you're awfully quiet.

00:48.085 --> 00:50.419
What word comes to your mind
when you think of Christmas?

00:51.354 --> 00:52.421
Lousy.

00:53.322 --> 00:54.723
Lousy?

00:54.725 --> 00:57.325
That doesn't sound very
Christmassy to me.

00:57.327 --> 00:59.995
Well, maybe she meant lousy
as in lousy the reindeer?

01:01.030 --> 01:02.731
There's no reindeer named lousy.

01:02.733 --> 01:05.000
She's right. It's drowsy.

01:05.001 --> 01:07.035
There's no reindeer
named drowsy either.

01:07.037 --> 01:10.072
Oh, yeah. I'm thinking
of the dwarves.

01:10.074 --> 01:11.773
You know, goldilocks
and the three dwarves.

01:11.775 --> 01:13.241
Lousy, drowsy, and Jim.

01:14.410 --> 01:16.411
Guys, we're trying to
write a song here.

01:16.413 --> 01:20.449
Christmas is about happiness and
being with the people you love.

01:20.451 --> 01:22.851
Yeah, Lily. Why would
you say it's lousy?

01:23.786 --> 01:26.254
I just think Christmas
is overrated.

01:26.256 --> 01:30.158
People make too big of a deal out of
it, and it's really not that great.

01:31.094 --> 01:32.160
It's lousy.

01:34.000 --> 01:40.074
